      <title>安机电在校外查成绩</title>
      <link href="/2019/an-ji-dian-zai-xiao-wai-cha-cheng-ji/"/>
      <url>/2019/an-ji-dian-zai-xiao-wai-cha-cheng-ji/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>（学校的虚拟专用网络好像出了些问题，此方法暂时无法使用）<br>教程准备:一台能联网的电脑或者手机、一双爪子、一个脑子<br>就直接就进入主题啦</p><h2 id="电脑教程"><a href="#电脑教程" class="headerlink" title="电脑教程"></a>电脑教程</h2><ol><li>访问 <a href="https://218.22.71.210:4433" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://218.22.71.210:4433</a> [电信用户] 或 <a href="https://111.38.190.131:4433" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://111.38.190.131:4433</a> [移动联通用户]（只能在外网访问，校园网内不能访问），提示证书有问题，不管它，点击“继续浏览此网站” <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lyl12321/picture/master/jidian/v_1.png" alt=""></li><li>输入自己的学号和密码，点击登录<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lyl12321/picture/master/jidian/v_2.png" alt=""></li><li>点击下载按钮下载山石VPN(这个将用于访问学校内网)<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lyl12321/picture/master/jidian/v_3.png" alt=""></li><li>打开后输入服务器地址:</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>标题</th><th>填入内容</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>电信用户服务器地址</td><td>218.22.71.210</td></tr><tr><td>移动联通服务器地址</td><td>111.38.190.131</td></tr><tr><td>端口号</td><td>4433</td></tr><tr><td>用户号</td><td>学号</td></tr><tr><td>密码</td><td>自己的密码</td></tr></tbody></table><ol start="5"><li>链接成功后托盘会显示: <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lyl12321/picture/master/jidian/v_4.png" alt=""></li><li>然后登录门户网站就可以查成绩了</li></ol><hr><h2 id="手机教程"><a href="#手机教程" class="headerlink" title="手机教程"></a>手机教程</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lyl12321/picture/master/jidian/rv_1.png" alt=""><br>手机用户就直接扫码下载APP，服务器地址和端口和上面一样</p><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
